item.title: Review of 'Steve Jobs and Bill Gates Face Off - YouTube' - Content delivery, AR
item.description: Original article Steve Jobs and Bill Gates Face Off - YouTube Content delivery Steve Jobs In some cases you know we have to do more work than others you know in the case of iTunes. There wasn’t a music delivery service that was any good so we had to do one. But in other cases there’s companies doing a way better job because we’re not as good at this stuff as other people are and we’d love to partner with them and we selectively do that.
